I wasn't able to find the location of all six world marathon majors, but here are the locations and dates of the first five I could find:

- The Tokyo Marathon, Tokyo, Japan: first held between 1980-1984
- The Boston Marathon, Boston, Massachusetts, US: first held 1897
- The London Marathon, London, UK: first held 1981
- The New York Marathon, New York, US: first held 1970
- The Chicago Marathon, Chicago, US: first held 1977

I found the Berlin Marathon in my search, which is one of the six world marathon majors, but I wasn't able to find out when it was first held.
